Ghana , Nigeria , Cameroon , and Namibia  arrive in Ivory Coast  for the Africa Cup of Nations in style.

Morocco  and Guinea-Bissau  were the first to arrive. Algeria , Tanzania , Egypt , and Mozambique  have also arrived.

More NAM Summit delegates, including ministerial representatives from Algeria and Angola, have arrived at the  Entebbe International Airport VVIP terminal.

- Nigeria, Cape Verde, Cameroon, Burkina Faso, Mali, DR Congo

To be best 3rd placed:
- Ghana, Guinea, South Africa, Zambia
